Now that we have those incredibly convenient popups for assigning issues, resolving issues, commenting etc, I find I almost never need to edit an issue -- except to set the Fix Version. 

It would be great to implement a popup (and shortcut) called "Schedule", allowing users to specify the Due Date, Fix Version (and maybe Affects Version).

