Defining a field configuration -- especially in an installation with lots of custom fields -- takes many times longer than it should.  Every Show/Hide/Required change causes a full screen update after which you then need to scroll back down to where you were.

Please change Show/Hide to be radio buttons and Required to be a checkbox and then provide a Save button to update all fields at once, or better yet Ajaxify the changes.  This would save a huge amount of admin's time.  Thanks.

